		<div class="info scrolling-right" id="about">
			<h1>About</h1>
			<br>
			<h2>How we began</h2>
			<p class="left">One fine October morning, with the cool wind blowing outside, a Khan Academy user named <a href="https://www.khanacademy.org/profile/kaid_3346337171905996578440529/">TorrentForce</a> had an idea as cool as the outdoor temperature.</p>
			<p class="left">This particular user had been on multiple teams, such as CodeX, Scriptara, and Team Coding Pros. He had had so much fun on those teams. But when they fell inactive, <a href="https://www.khanacademy.org/profile/kaid_3346337171905996578440529/">TorrentForce</a> got bored.<br>His idea was: <strong>He would make his <em>own</em> team!</strong></p>
			<p class="left">So <a href="https://www.khanacademy.org/profile/kaid_3346337171905996578440529/">TorrentForce</a> set to work, creating a team homepage using Python, the programming language he knew the most.</p>
			<p class="left">Once that was done, <a href="https://www.khanacademy.org/profile/kaid_3346337171905996578440529/">TorrentForce</a> invited several users to join the team. All accepted, and Team Omega Primes had officially begun.</p>
			<h2>The terrible inactivity</h2>
			<p class="left">Soon after the team's success, however, <a href="https://www.khanacademy.org/profile/kaid_3346337171905996578440529/">TorrentForce</a> announced that he would become inactive! Soon after <a href="https://www.khanacademy.org/profile/kaid_3346337171905996578440529/">TorrentForce</a> fell inactive, so did the entire team! It looked as if Team Omega Primes was on the verge of falling apart.</p>
			<h2>The team rises again</h2>
			<p class="left">Thankfully, under the leadership of <a href="https://www.khanacademy.org/profile/kaid_677611614554857766314873">MMS Matthew360°</a>, Team Omega Primes continued to stand.</p>
			<p class="left">Then, <a href="https://www.khanacademy.org/profile/kaid_3346337171905996578440529/">TorrentForce</a> returned, with new knowledge of HTML and CSS! He and <a href="https://www.khanacademy.org/profile/kaid_6399133970940964287498062">Hooray X.</a> built a new homepage using HTML and CSS.<br>Soon, after the team's victory, <a href="https://www.khanacademy.org/profile/kaid_829234581759719945657916">Pinkcatsoda</a>, a skilled programmer-artist, also joined the team. It seemed that the glorious days would never end.</p>
			<h2>The Christmas Blizzard</h2>
			<p class="left">But around Christmas, the team faced yet another crucial challenge. Then important admin <a href="https://www.khanacademy.org/profile/kaid_677611614554857766314873">M.M.S. (Matthew360)</a> went semi-inactive, soon followed by <a href="https://www.khanacademy.org/profile/kaid_829234581759719945657916">Pinkcatsoda</a> and <a href="https://www.khanacademy.org/profile/kaid_3346337171905996578440529/">TorrentForce</a> too. Just when things were looking terrible, <a href="https://www.khanacademy.org/profile/kaid_578661680921733406040161">DebugRanger</a> decided to join because he thought this team needed help. <a href="https://www.khanacademy.org/profile/kaid_1186408866140234333238044">Lord Familia</a> and <a href="https://www.khanacademy.org/profile/kaid_1078378520650574901650073">1001programmer1001</a> joined too.<br>With the help of the new members, the team rose again, with important admin <a href="https://www.khanacademy.org/profile/kaid_6399133970940964287498062">Hooray X.</a> updating the homepage to look even cooler!</p>
			<h2>The New Year Rush</h2>
			<p class="left">Since the start of the new year, 3 members have joined Team Omega Primes within the first week of 2026! This was probably one of T.O.P.'s greatest weeks. Say hello to <a href="https://www.khanacademy.org/profile/kaid_1078378520650574901650073">1001programmer1001</a>, <a href="https://www.khanacademy.org/profile/kaid_1186408866140234333238044">Lord Familia</a>, and <a href="https://www.khanacademy.org/profile/kaid_4157025907581241548995475">Fi fi fo fum</a>!</p>
			<h2>Contest Summoning</h2>
			<p class="left">Soon, new users started swarming in thanks to <a href="https://www.khanacademy.org/profile/kaid_1078378520650574901650073">1001programmer1001</a>'s posters and our games. <a href="https://www.khanacademy.org/profile/kaid_394298844827230785358833">Rain</a>, <a href="https://www.khanacademy.org/profile/kaid_5269884588402240227278291">Lettuce the Great Parrot🥨🦜</a>, <a href="https://www.khanacademy.org/profile/kaid_12292242763670672864943">Borbonbaseball17</a>, <a href="https://www.khanacademy.org/profile/kaid_4815615438153162796364791">Shadow</a>, <a href="https://www.khanacademy.org/profile/kaid_8259026998720596700468501">Akh</a>,<br><a href="https://www.khanacademy.org/profile/kaid_413575084497159272792117">caleb.catt</a>, <a href="https://www.khanacademy.org/profile/kaid_379384843910705248659233">Exospacer</a>, <a href="https://www.khanacademy.org/profile/kaid_2866649053533900543633356">JustLord</a>, and <a href="https://www.khanacademy.org/profile/kaid_683269329038607171911600">Robby</a> joined the team. <a href="https://www.khanacademy.org/profile/kaid_6399133970940964287498062">Hooray X.</a> hosted the Contest: Planetoid and <a href="https://www.khanacademy.org/profile/kaid_1078378520650574901650073">1001programmer1001</a> came out on top!</p>
			<h2>Ocean Exploring</h2>
			<p><a href="https://www.khanacademy.org/profile/kaid_3346337171905996578440529/">TorrentForce</a> created projects Snake I and Snake II and successfully reached over 30 votes. This victory gave us the idea for a JS project that could rival Team Quantum Cat's CoC final Abyssal. We started the project Ocean Before Time, with most of the team helping. We were surprised how popular it was even when it was a menu without any real game, getting 38 votes. And just like that, we attracted the users <a href="https://www.khanacademy.org/profile/kaid_878332344750460734130956">Josephine❤︎</a>, <a href="https://www.khanacademy.org/profile/kaid_574576985099042639713735">GᴀʟᴀxʏRᴀɴɢᴇʀ</a>, <a href="https://www.khanacademy.org/profile/kaid_336838091572425251271773/">ϮԋϵϾԋᴉͼҝϵлѪαϟϯϵπ</a>, and <a href="https://www.khanacademy.org/profile/kaid_434226319389036660332874">Fluffy (≖⩊≖)</a>. At the time, <a href="https://www.khanacademy.org/profile/kaid_394298844827230785358833">Rain</a>, the Brainstormer Head, created a pixel art poster attracting a portion of the members mentioned above.</p>
			<h2>HTML Reckoning</h2>
			<p>While most of the team worked on Ocean before time,Hooray X. and Rain decided to do some HTML.As Hooray X. made yet <em>another</em> update on this cool and spectacular homepage,Rain created inspirational posters to Join T.O.P.. Hooray X. started making a 3D Platformer and together with Rain's posters to get 6 new members,<a href="https://www.khanacademy.org/profile/kaid_82898098000024228278987">SWΛNKYᴍᴀɴ
				</a>,<a href="https://www.khanacademy.org/profile/kaid_874151668702033138605965">Ϊ∯Λ∀ΞΠΘΠΛ₼Ξ</a>,<a href="https://www.khanacademy.org/profile/kaid_250216876308675101675883">Anonymous</a>,<a href="https://www.khanacademy.org/profile/kaid_521789616340270471323300">Ikorac🔥
				</a>,<a href="https://www.khanacademy.org/profile/kaid_216276079253098825743247">Blueburst
				</a>,<a href="https://www.khanacademy.org/profile/kaid_216276079253098825743247">FancyBoy
				</a>and <a href="https://www.khanacademy.org/profile/kaid_466731574472354573012698">Dragon Studios🔥🐦🐉🐍
				</a></p>
