			<p>After posting, wait for an admin to review your coding level and approve your membership.</p>
			<p>An admin will decide your coding level.</p>
			<h2>Coding Levels</h2>
			<p>These coding levels determine your programming skill progress in Team Omega Primes.</p>
			<h3>Alpha Coder</h3>
			<p>Alpha coders have basic skill and may need assistance from more advanced programmers.</p>
			<h3>Pro-alpha coder</h3>
			<p>Pro-alpha coders are improving quickly and can complete small-to-medium tasks more independently.</p>
			<h3>Deltagrammer</h3>
			<p>Deltagrammers are capable and can build many projects with little or no assistance.</p>
			<h3>Pro-deltagrammer</h3>
			<p>Pro-deltagrammers are strong contributors who consistently deliver reliable coding work.</p>
			<h3>Sigma-deltagrammer</h3>
			<p>Sigma-deltagrammers are high-level coders trusted with harder tasks and advanced teamwork.</p>
			<h3>Proto-omicronner</h3>
			<p>Proto-omicronners are near-top coders who are preparing for full omicronner responsibility.</p>
			<h3>Omicronner</h3>
			<p>Omicronners are advanced and highly skilled programmers who help guide less advanced members.</p>
			<h3>Special Rank Ladder</h3>
			<p>After Omicronner, leadership and admin titles continue as: Co-leader/head, Leader/Head, Pro-admin, Admin, and Omega Prime.</p>
			<br>
			<p>Do not be afraid to ask for help, even if you are an Omicronner!</p>
			<br>
			<h2>Other Ranks</h2>
			<h3>Brainstorming Leader</h3>
			<p>The Brainstorming Leader title is awarded to a member who consistently contributes exceptional creativity, strong ideas, and imaginative thinking. This position is currently held by <a href="https://www.khanacademy.org/profile/kaid_568053311456555725201444/discussion">ℝ𝕒𝕚𝕟</a>.</p><br>
			<h3>Processing JS Head</h3>
			<p>The Processing JS Head title is reserved for a highly skilled, productive, and dependable programmer with strong Processing JS experience. This position is currently held by <a href="https://www.khanacademy.org/profile/kaid_578661680921733406040161">DebugRanger</a>.</p><br>
			<h3>Co-Processing JS Leader</h3>
			<p>The Co-Processing JS Leader supports Processing JS leadership and recognizes strong ability and continued contribution in that area. This position is currently held by <a href="https://www.khanacademy.org/profile/kaid_574576985099042639713735">GᴀʟᴀxʏRᴀɴɢᴇʀ</a>. His main flaw is limited activity.</p><br>
			<h3>HTML/CSS Hyperion</h3>
			<p>The HTML/CSS Hyperion rank is given to a member who helps improve the homepage and demonstrates strong HTML and CSS knowledge, consistency, and responsibility. This position is currently held by <a href="https://www.khanacademy.org/profile/kaid_683269329038607171911600">Hooray X.</a>.</p><br>
			<h3>Python Omega</h3>
			<p>The Python Omega title is intended for a member with outstanding Python ability and a strong record of high-quality work. This position belongs to our leader - <a href="https://www.khanacademy.org/profile/kaid_3346337171905996578440529">TorrentForce</a>!</p><br>
			<h3>Art Corona</h3>
			<p>The Art Corona is gave to an active and supportive graphics artist. He or she must have a history of memorial artworks in his or her profile. This position belongs to <a href="https://www.khanacademy.org/profile/kaid_829234581759719945657916">PinkCatSoda</a>.</p><br>
			<h3>HTML Builder</h3>
			<p>The HTML Builder is a rank for another member that is good at HTML and can be used instead of HTM/CSS Hyperion when he is unavailable.This rank is currently under the ownership of <a href="https://www.khanacademy.org/profile/kaid_4157025907581241548995475">Fi fi fo fum</a>.</p><br>
			<h3>Animation Origo</h3>
			<p>The Animation Origo makes animations in HTML/Pjs for the teams needs. He or she must prove themselves proficient of the title. This animator is <a href="https://www.khanacademy.org/profile/kaid_466731574472354573012698">Dragon Studios 🐉 🐦🔥 🐍</a>.</p><br>
			<h3>Project Inspector</h3>
			<p>The Project Inspector inspects projects member made for bugs and fixes.He/She also decides if a certain program or joining time margin is enough for a members rank up to pro-admin. This person is none other than <a href="https://www.khanacademy.org/profile/kaid_677611614554857766314873">MMS Matthew360</a>.</p><br>
			<h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
			<h3>Can anyone join Team Omega Primes?</h3>
			<p><strong>Answer:</strong> YES! Anyone, at any skill level, can join Team Omega Primes!</p>
			<h3>How do I become an admin?</h3>
			<p><strong>Answer:</strong> To become an admin, you have to be picked by the Omega Prime (<a href="https://www.khanacademy.org/profile/kaid_3346337171905996578440529/">TorrentForce</a>).<br> Admins have to be hard-working, sociable, and active. <br><strong>Current Admins:</strong> <a href="https://www.khanacademy.org/profile/kaid_677611614554857766314873">MMS (Matthew360°)</a>, <a href="https://www.khanacademy.org/profile/kaid_6399133970940964287498062">Hooray X.</a> and <a href="https://www.khanacademy.org/profile/kaid_568053311456555725201444/discussion">ℝ𝕒𝕚𝕟</a>.</p><!-- Hooray X. is not sociable tho -->
			<h3>Can anyone become the Omega Prime?</h3>
			<p><strong>Answer:</strong> No. The rank "Omega Prime" is reserved to the founder of the team. However, you can still become an admin!</p>
